#: build/admin/airygen-app.js
msgid "Broken Link Checker"
msgstr "失效連結檢查器"

#: build/admin/airygen-app.js
msgid "Scan content for broken and redirected links, and monitor crawl health."
msgstr "掃描內容以尋找失效和重新導向的連結，並監控檢索健康狀況。"

#: build/admin/airygen-app.js
msgid "Link Counter must be enabled to gather internal link data."
msgstr "必須啟用連結計數器才能收集內部連結資料。"

#: build/admin/airygen-app.js
msgid "Tune scan frequency and limits. Lower numbers are safer on shared hosts."
msgstr "調整掃描頻率和限制。較低的數字在共享主機上更安全。"

#: build/admin/airygen-app.js
msgid "How often the scanner runs. Set higher on large sites."
msgstr "掃描器執行的頻率。在大型網站上設定更高。"

#: build/admin/airygen-app.js
msgid "Max requests per run"
msgstr "每次執行的最大請求數"

#: build/admin/airygen-app.js
msgid "Limits simultaneous HTTP requests during a scan."
msgstr "限制掃描期間的同時 HTTP 請求數。"

#: build/admin/airygen-app.js
msgid "Pause between request batches to reduce load."
msgstr "在請求批次之間暫停以減少負載。"

#: build/admin/airygen-app.js
msgid "Older log entries are deleted automatically."
msgstr "較舊的紀錄項目會自動刪除。"

#: build/admin/airygen-app.js
msgid "Max time to open a connection before aborting."
msgstr "中止前開啟連線的最長時間。"

#: build/admin/airygen-app.js
msgid "Max time to complete a request before aborting."
msgstr "中止前完成請求的最長時間。"

#: build/admin/airygen-app.js
msgid "Treat redirects as warnings"
msgstr "將重新導向視為警告"

#: build/admin/airygen-app.js
msgid "When on, redirected links are flagged but not counted as errors."
msgstr "開啟時，重新導向的連結會被標記但不算作錯誤。"

#: build/admin/airygen-app.js
msgid "Choose which link types are included in broken-link scans."
msgstr "選擇失效連結掃描要包含哪些連結類型。"

#: build/admin/airygen-app.js
msgid "Link types to scan"
msgstr "要掃描的連結類型"

#: build/admin/airygen-app.js
